<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            padding-top: 100px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404 - Page Not Found</h1>
        <p>Oops! The page you are looking for might have been removed or is temporarily unavailable.</p>
        <p>Return to the <a href="/">homepage</a>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
